\c 29
\nb
\v 1 UDavida inkosi wasesithi ebandleni lonke: USolomoni indodana yami, yena yedwa uNkulunkulu amkhethileyo, u\add se\add*ngumfana ubuthakathaka\x + 22.5.\x*, lomsebenzi mkhulu; ngoba isigodlo kayisiso somuntu, kodwa ngeseN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu\x + 29.19. Neh. 2.8. 7.2. Ezra 6.2. Neh. 1.1. Esta 1.2,5. 2.3,5,8. Dan. 8.2.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho ngiyilungisele indlu kaNkulunkulu wami ngamandla ami wonke, igolide lo\add kwe\add*golide, lesiliva lo\add kwe\add*siliva, lethusi lo\add kwe\add*thusi, insimbi lo\add kwe\add*nsimbi, lezigodo lo\add kwe\add*zigodo, amatshe \w e-onikse\w**\x + Gen. 2.12.\x* lawokubekwa\x + Eks. 25.7. 35.9,27.\x*, amatshe akhazimulayo lalemibala\x + Isa. 54.11.\x*, lenhlobo zonke zamatshe aligugu\x + Hez. 17.3.\x*, lamatshe \w e-alibasta\w** ngobunengi\x + Esta 1.6.\x*.
\v 3 Laphezu kwakho, ngenxa yokuthanda kwami indlu kaNkulunkulu wami, nganikela indlu kaNkulunkulu wami inotho yegolide leyesiliva, engilakho, phezu kwakho konke engikulungisele indlu yendawo engcwele,
\v 4 \w amathalenta\w** egolide azinkulungwane ezintathu egolideni\x + 22.14.\x* leOfiri\x + 1 Kho. 9.28.\x*, \w lamathalenta\w** esiliva elicwengekileyo\x + 28.18.\x* azinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, ukuhuqa imiduli yezindlu.
\v 5 Igolide kusenzelwa \add okwe\add*golide, lesiliva kusenzelwa \add okwe\add*siliva, langawo wonke umsebenzi ngesandla sezingcitshi. Ngubani-ke ovumayo ukuzehlukanisela iN\nd kosi\nd* lamuhla?
\p
\v 6 Inhloko zaboyise zasezinikela ngesihle, lezinduna zezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 27.1. 28.1.\x*, labaphathi bezinkulungwane labamakhulu, labaphathi bomsebenzi wenkosi\x + 27.25-31.\x*.
\v 7 Basebenikela emsebenzini wendlu kaNkulunkulu \w amathalenta\w** azinkulungwane ezinhlanu egolide, lenhlamvu ezizinkulungwane ezilitshumi, \w lamathalenta\w** esiliva azinkulungwane ezilitshumi, \w lamathalenta\w** ethusi azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lesificaminwembili, \w lamathalenta\w** ensimbi azinkulungwane ezilikhulu\x + Ezra 8.27. Ezra 2.69. Neh. 7.70,71,72.\x*.
\v 8 Lalabo okwatholwa kibo amatshe aligugu bawanika indlu yokuligugu yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 29.2.\x* ngaphansi kwesandla\x + 23.8.\x* sikaJehiyeli umGerishoni\x + 25.2.\x*.
\v 9 Basebethokoza abantu ngokunikela kwabo ngesihle, ngoba ngenhliziyo epheleleyo babenikele ngothando kuNkulunkulu; loDavida inkosi laye wathokoza ngentokozo enkulu\x + 2 Kho. 12.4. 2 Kor. 9.7.\x*.
\s UDavida ubonga iN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 10 UDavida waseyibusisa iN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kwamehlo ebandla lonke; uDavida wathi: Kawubusiswe wena N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ubaba, kusukela ephakadeni kuze kube sephakadeni\x + Luka 1.68.\x*.
\v 11 Kungokwakho, N\nd kosi\nd*, ubukhulu\x + Dute. 3.24.\x* lamandla\x + Mat. 6.13. 1 Tim. 1.17. Isam. 5.13.\x* lodumo\x + Mat. 6.13. 1 Tim. 1.17. Isam. 5.13.\x* lokunqoba lobukhosi; ngoba konke okusemazulwini lokusemhlabeni \add kungokwakho\add*; umbuso ungowakho, N\nd kosi\nd*; wena uziphakamisile waba yinhloko phezu kwakho konke\x + Mat. 6.13. 1 Tim. 1.17. Isam. 5.13.\x*.
\v 12 Lenotho lodumo kuvela phambi kwakho, wena-ke ubusa phezu kwakho konke\x + Roma 11.35,36.\x*; lesandleni sakho kukhona ukuqina lamandla, lesandleni sakho kukhona ukukhulisa lokupha amandla kubo bonke\x + 2 Lan. 20.6.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho-ke Nkulunkulu wethu, siyakubonga, silidumise ibizo lakho elilodumo.
\v 14 Ngoba mina-ke ngingubani, labantu bami bangobani, ukuthi sithole amandla okunika ngothando ngokunje? Ngoba konke kuvela kuwe, sinikele kuwe okuvela esandleni sakho.
\v 15 Ngoba singabemzini phambi kwakho labahlala njengabezizwe njengabo bonke obaba\x + Hlab. 39.12. Hlab. 90.9. Levi 25.23.\x*; insuku zethu emhlabeni zinjengesithunzi, njalo kalikho ithemba\x + Jobe 14.2. Hlab. 102.11. 144. 4.\x*.
\v 16 N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wethu, konke lokhu okunengi, esikulungisele ukwakhela wena indlu, kusenzelwa ibizo lakho elingcwele, kuvela esandleni sakho, njalo konke kungokwakho.
\v 17 Ngiyazi-ke, Nkulunkulu wami, ukuthi wena uhlola inhliziyo\x + 28.9. Zaga 17.3. 1 Sam. 16.7.\x*, uyabuthanda ubuqotho\x + Zaga 11.20.\x*. Mina, ebuqothweni benhliziyo yami nginikele ngesihle zonke lezizinto; khathesi sengibonile ngentokozo abantu bakho abatholakala lapha ukuthi banikela kuwe ngesihle\x + 29.9.\x*.
\v 18 N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uIsaka, loIsrayeli, obaba, gcina lokho laphakade ekuzindleni kweminakano yenhliziyo yabantu bakho, ulungise inhliziyo yabo kuwe\x + 28.9.\x*.
\v 19 Njalo unike uSolomoni indodana yami inhliziyo epheleleyo ukugcina imilayo yakho, ubufakazi bakho, lezimiso zakho\x + 29.9. 1 Kho. 8.61.\x*, lokwenza konke, lokwakha isigodlo\x + 29.1.\x* engisilungise\add le\add*leyo\x + 29.2. 22.14.\x*.
\s Abantu babeka uSolomoni ukuba yinkosi
\p
\v 20 UDavida wasesithi kulo lonke ibandla: Khathesi busisani iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu. Ibandla lonke laselibusisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + Josh. 22.33.\x*; bakhothama bamkhonza uJehova, lenkosi\x + Eks. 4.31.\x*.
\v 21 Basebehlabela imihlatshelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngokusa kwalolosuku, amajongosi azinkulungwane, izinqama eziyinkulungwane, amawundlu ayinkulungwane, kanye leminikelo yabo yokunathwayo, lemihlatshelo ngobunengi kusenzelwa uIsrayeli wonke\x + Gen. 35.14.\x*.
\v 22 Basebesidla banatha phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngalolosuku ngentokozo enkulu. Basebembeka okwesibili\x + 23.1.\x* uSolomoni indodana kaDavida ukuthi abe yinkosi, ba\add m\add*gcobela iN\nd kosi\nd* waba ngumkhokheli\x + 1 Kho. 1.33-39.\x*, loZadoki waba ngumpristi\x + 23.1.\x*.
\v 23 USolomoni\x + 1 Kho. 2.12,35. 2 Lan. 1.1.\x* wasehlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaJehova njengenkosi esikhundleni sikaDavida uyise, waphumelela; loIsrayeli wonke wamlalela\x + 28.5. 2 Lan. 9.8. 13.8.\x*.
\v 24 Lazo zonke izinduna lamaqhawe kanye lawo wonke amadodana enkosi uDavida bazehlisela\f + \fk bazehlisela: \fl Heb. \fq banika isandla ngaphansi kukaSolomoni.\f* ngaphansi kukaSolomoni inkosi.
\v 25 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimphakamisa uSolomoni kakhulu phambi kwamehlo kaIsrayeli wonke\x + 2 Lan. 1.1. Josh. 3.7.\x*, yamnika ubukhosi bombuso obungazanga bube khona lakuyiphi inkosi ngaphambi kwakhe koIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 3.13. 2 Lan. 1.12. Tshu. 2.9.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ngokunjalo uDavida indodana kaJese wayebuse phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke.
\v 27 Njalo insuku abusa ngazo phezu kukaIsrayeli zaziyiminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 2 Sam. 5.4. 1 Kho. 2.11.\x*; eHebroni wabusa iminyaka eyisikhombisa, leJerusalema wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lantathu\x + 2 Sam. 5.5.\x*.
\v 28 Wasesifa eseluphele kuhle\x + Gen. 15.15. 25.8.\x*, enele ngezinsuku, inotho lodumo; uSolomoni indodana yakhe wasebusa esikhundleni sakhe\x + 23.1.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo izindaba zikaDavida inkosi, ezokuqala lezokucina\x + 2 Lan. 9.29. 12.15. 16.11. 20.34. 25.26. 26.22. 28.26. 35.27.\x*, khangela, zibhaliwe egwalweni lwezindaba zikaSamuweli umboni\x + 26.28. 1 Sam. 9.9.\x* legwalweni lwezindaba zikaNathani umprofethi\x + 2 Sam. 12.1.\x* legwalweni lwezindaba zikaGadi\x + 1 Sam. 22.5.\x* umboni\x + 2 Lan. 19.2. 29.25,30. 33.18,19. 35.15. 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*,
\v 30 kanye lakho konke ukubusa kwakhe lamandla akhe, lezikhathi ezedlula phezu kwakhe laphezu kukaIsrayeli laphezu kwayo yonke imibuso yamazwe\x + Dan. 4.23,25.\x*.